.It Ev MAILRC
Pathname of file containing initial
.Nm
commands.
Default is
.Pa ~/.mailrc .
.It Ev MBOX
The name of the mailbox file.
It can be the name of a folder.
The default is
.Pa mbox
in the user's home directory.
.It Ev PAGER
Pathname of the program to use in the
.Ic more
command or when
.Va crt
variable is set.
