.Xr less 1
is used if this option is not defined.
.It Ev REPLYTO
If set, will be used to initialize the Reply-To field for outgoing
messages.
.It Ev SHELL
Pathname of the shell to use in the
.Ic \&!
command and the
.Ic ~!
escape.
