not defined.
.It Ev TMPDIR
Pathname of the directory used for creating temporary files.
.It Ev VISUAL
Pathname of the text editor to use in the
.Ic visual
command and
.Ic ~v
escape.
.It Ev USER
Login name of the user executing mail.
